# Sparkle signing key. The PUBLIC half (assets/sparkle-public-key.txt) is
# committed on purpose — every build embeds it to verify updates. The PRIVATE
# half must never be: whoever holds it can ship code to every user. It lives in
# the login Keychain, and `generate_keys -x` exports it here temporarily when
# backing it up, which is exactly when an `git add -A` would otherwise catch it.
*private-key*
*private_key*
sparkle-private*
